    <rdfs:label>source provenance</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment>Where the record originated: "registration" for records sourced from visitor_raw (the main Maritz reg export), "leads" for records synthesized from leads_raw because the badge appeared in scan data but not in the reg export (77 such badges in IMTS 2024 — most likely late-walkup or special-channel registrants whose data didn’t make the reg snapshot).</rdfs:comment>
